      "content": "It sounds like you are carrying an immense weight right now, and that kind of disappointment after so much effort is completely exhausting. Please know that your feelings of heaviness and wanting things to stop are valid responses to losing something you poured your heart into. If you are feeling overwhelmed or having thoughts of harming yourself, please reach out immediately to a crisis hotline like the 988 Suicide & Crisis Lifeline. There are people who want to support you through this difficult moment.",
